on your way up? And if so do you have many chanters that are contesting the epic drop? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uelazulvaleren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elazul Valeren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(8/7/02 8:25:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=566.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoH raid - Sunday Aug 3rd - KoE</span><hr size=1> Hate was a no-go Sardus, however we will be attempting it again soon (not going to say when yet because of uber guilds fu*king us over). We will do as many Forsaken Revenants as possible but we only have 2 chanters contesting for the piece. One has been at it a long time though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/unydiaywalmoriel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nydia Ywalmoriel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(8/8/02 1:11:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=566.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoH raid - Sunday Aug 3rd - KoE</span><hr size=1> Dear Sardus:<br><br>The first floor of Hate is easily doable by 1- 1 1/2 groups, if you're just going for revs.  From my own experience, going on big raids is a bad way to try to get this drop, because it *is* rare, and the chances that there are going to be another enchanter on the raid who needs the drop (and are further along on epic/higher level, if your guild uses such a system) are very high.  <br><br>My advice to you is to get a regular exp group (FD puller a must) going up there on off nights, with the goal of pulling as many of these guys as possible (they mostly spawn on the first floor in the buildings in the northeast part of the zone).  I haven't seen that essence drop yet, but have gotten nearly a full set of Insidious... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br><br>Best of luck,<br>Nydia Ywalmoriel<br>Autonomous Collective <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/umagoliss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Magoliss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wanderer</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(8/9/02 5:42:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=566.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoH raid - Sunday Aug 3rd - KoE</span><hr size=1> Are you guys planning on hitting magi' ptasa? If so and no other mages need staff Ill go <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>-Mag <br>54th Mage <p><a href="http://geocities.com/clansilverhammer/" target="_blank"><img src="http://geocities.com/clansilverhammer/Wanted2.jpg" border="0"></a><BR>Your faction standing with damn near everything can't possibly get any worse.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uelazulvaleren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elazul Valeren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(8/16/02 10:58:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=566.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoH raid - Sunday Aug 3rd - KoE</span><hr size=1> Our purpose for Hate for now is just letting some of the guildies get to know Hate that dont already and to pharm first floor armor and gems. If you're looking for mini boss killings and such you'll have to talk to another guild. Sorry.<br><br>Though, good news is we got one of our chanters the revanent drop that he needed and thus we only have one guild chanter left to get the piece. Gratz Elemak! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=566.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=566.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=566.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.threadControl?topicID=566.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=566.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=566.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub42.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="ayonaerofrm1">General Forum<option valu